measurements.description: Two flowers on two up to 30-cm inflorescences; dorsal sepal slightly undulate, obovate, ciliate, hirsute on adaxial surface, chartreuse, overlaid maroon proximally; synsepal obovate, slightly undulate, ciliate, hirsute on adaxial surface, veined maroon centrally; petals ciliate, spatulate, undulate, reflexed distally, chartreuse, spotted maroon proximally, overlaid bright lavender distally, margin dark lavender; pouch chartreuse, lightly overlaid light maroon, stippled maroon upper half; staminode chartreuse, overlaid maroon proximally, umbo chartreuse; substance medium; texture glossy.
